title: Start with WHY for Retirees - March 25, 2022
description:
What is Start with WHY for Retirees?
You’ve already had a full career and now you’re contemplating what could be next for an encore chapter. Sometimes, the best way to plan ahead is to, first, look back.

This interactive class is designed to walk you, step-by-step, through the process to find your WHY – your personal purpose, cause or belief. You will explore who you have been when at your natural best, throughout your life and career, so that you can design your next chapter on your own terms. You will work in a community of like-minded peers to help one another put into words the cause you care most about advancing and how you can use your life and career as a vehicle to do so. It takes a willingness to be open, to share personal stories and to trust the process. And through it all, we’re there to help.

In this class you will:

 	Unpack the concept of The Golden Circle from Start With Why and apply it to your next life chapter
 	Collaborate with a peer to discover and develop your WHY statement in a 1:1 environment
 	Explore the talents and skill sets that tend to improve with age
 	Benefit from live coaching to help you improve and apply your WHY statement
